Package: deepin-traffic-toll
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         iproute2,
         kmod
Description: Process-level network traffic control tool
 A C++ implementation of network traffic control tool using Linux TC
 (Traffic Control) and HTB (Hierarchy Token Bucket) queue disciplines.
 .
 Features:
  - Process-level bandwidth limiting for specific applications
  - Traffic priority control for critical applications
  - Flexible process matching via name, path, or command line regex
  - Recursive process matching for Electron/Chromium apps
  - Minimum bandwidth guarantee
  - Optional automatic speed detection
  - Dynamic configuration update
